essie: all the wave Über die Osterfeiertage sind mein ♥-Mann und ich das erste Mal zusammen weg gefahren - und wie ... Nagellack-Fotos auch die eine oder andere Impression von unserem kleinen Köln-Trip untergemischt. 'all the wave' ist aus der diesjährigen Spring-Kollektion von essie und für mich beinahe eher ein Lack für den Sommer... Dieses Blau hat meiner Meinung nach schon etwas von Meer ... man eben einfach nicht drumherum! ♥ Noch dazu ist 'all the wave' wesentlich klarer, tiefer und schöner als einige andere essie-Blaus, 'mezmerised' zum Beispiel.Ich hoffe, ihr habt die Ostertage erholsam mit euren Lieben verbracht oder etwas anderes gemacht, was euch glücklich

Esmalte Essie 1046: um glitter poderoso Eu estou sumida sim, ou com certeza? Com 2017 veio ainda mais correria na minha vida ... frequência normal. Para começar, nada melhor do que mostrar um esmalte bonito, não é mesmo? Hoje eu mostro o esmalte Essie 1046, um esmalte com acabamento de glitter e de cor bem poderosa.
Essie 1046



O esmalte possui um tom de vinho puxado para o magenta muito bonito e vem carregado de glitter – ... brilho do glitter e muito brilho do top coat, ou seja, só amor.
Quanto eu paguei?
Eu comprei o esmalte Essie 1046 em uma loja de cosméticos aqui no Rio de Janeiro e ele foi R$19,00 na época.

euch nicht unter diesem Motto vorzustellen!Sweet Darling stammt aus dem Standardsortiment von p2 und wurde vor langer Zeit mal als Essie-Dupe gehypet. Ob er heute noch erhältlich ist, kann ich euch leider nicht mit Sicherheit sagen. Ich selbst habe den Lack ... ich noch mehrere ähnliche Ausfertigungen. Verglichen wurde Sweet Darling stets mit Lilacism, der für mich fast ein bisschen zu den Essie-Klassikern gehört. Dem ähnelt er tatsächlich zu 99%, nur kommt mir die günstigere Version ein klitzekleines Bisschen weniger Blau vor. Dass ... Nice ein ganzes Stückchen heller ist, sieht man ja deutlich.Im Auftrag würde ich die günstigere Version der Farbe eindeutig dem Essie vorziehen! Ich bin ja generell kein großer Fan der Essie-Qualität, sondern fühle mich immer mehr von den Farben angesprochen. Die Pinsel sind zwar durchweg super, die Konsistenz aber leider immer ... und p2 beweist das hier mal wieder ziemlich gut!Wie seht ihr das? Gehört ihr noch zu denen, die deutlich hinter Essie stehen?xoxo; Sophe.

I 10 smalti Essie più venduti di sempre: ecco i must-have della manicure Essie è ormai un brand cult per quanto riguarda gli smalti, e sappiamo che moltissime di voi ne sono appassionate. Quando ci siamo imbattute, quindi, nella lista dei 10 smalti Essie più venduti di sempre (pubblicata dal sito essieenvy.com), abbiamo pensato che potesse essere interessante per chi vuole ampliare la propria collezione.
Se siete a caccia di ispirazioni per ... i gusti. Abbiamo sfumature classiche e più particolari, nude pastello e colori più audaci. Se anche voi amate gli smalti Essie, o volete provarne uno, andate avanti a leggere!
Gli swatches degli smalti sono tratti da @essieenvy.com

#1 MUCHI, MUCHI, SMALTO PEONY PINK

Essie Muchi Muchi. Su Amazon.it a 8,72€
Si tratta di uno smalto uscito ormai 10 anni fa, nel 2007, in una ... simile a quel Peony Pink che quest’anno spopola nella moda e nel makeup.

#2 LO SMALTO BIANCO PIÙ CLASSICO: BLANC

Essie Blanc. Su Amazon.it a 8,72€
È il più classico degli smalti “color scolorina” ;-D! Nessuna sorpresa che Blanc compaia in ... e matt.
IL TREND DELLO SMALTO BIANCO, DOPO ANNI È ANCORA ATTUALISSIMO
Blanc fa parte delle prime 12 nuance che Essie Weingarten creò nel lontano 1981. Se avete una buona manualità, risulta molto coprente anche con due passate.
È fantastico se sopra mettete un top coat brillante, come Good To Go sempre di Essie o il nostro amato Gel Coat di Essence.

#3 SMOKIN’HOT: ELEGANTE E UNICO

Essie Smokin’Hot. Su Amazon.it a 8,72€
Forse è il più inaspettato tra i 10 smalti best seller di Essie, ma se lo avete capirete che non lo è poi così tanto. Il colore è meraviglioso, insolito, elegante, inimitabile.
Smokin’Hot ... un finish lucido e impeccabile con due passate, tre se non siete esperte.
#4 IL ROSA ACCESO DI ETERNAL OPTIMIST

Essie Eternal Optimist. Su Amazon.it a 11,49€
Un’altra sfumatura tra le più famose del brand è un rosa particolarissimo, tra il ... cremoso e su alcune carnagioni e la luce giusta può quasi sembrare un nude.

#5 WICKED, DUPE DI ROUGE NOIR

Essie Wicked. Su Amazon.it a 8,72€
Non poteva mancare in questa lista di must-have Wicked, considerato il dupe di Rouge Noir ... dura a lungo ed è perfetto in due passate.

Ragazze, siamo a metà nella lista dei best seller di casa Essie. La prossima parte del post manderà in brodo di giuggiole chi ama gli smalti rosa e nude… ma non deluderà nemmeno chi predilige le tinte più vivaci ;-)! Girate pagina!

The Beauty Review: Revlon Colourstay Gel Envy 
You know how everyone love that most iconic of nail polishes, Essie’s Ballet Slippers? It was recently revealed that even Her Majesty, Queen Elizabeth II wears only Essie Ballet Slippers on her impeccably manicured fingers. Every celebrity loves it, you hear about it all the time, but you know what?
I HATE it.
There. I said it. I hate Essie Ballet Slippers like no other nail polish I’ve tried. Now don’t get me wrong, you know I love my Essie polishes (as seen here, here, and here), but Ballet Slippers is one that has always driven me crazy. Am I ... wipe it off furiously, wondering why I even tried.

I will add this one little aside, in case anyone from Essie Canada happens to be reading – can we make the brush just a wee bit wider? I love the colours ... Colorstay Gel Envy shades, but I can tell you that if you have also struggled with the final finish of Essie’s Ballet Slippers but you desperately want that colour, you cannot go wrong with this one. de uñas que no sea un rosa neutro. Este rosa pálido es llamado 'Ballet Slippers'  y pertenece a la marca Essie, el cual ha sido utilizado por la reina Isabel II desde 1989. Según la marca de belleza, la peluquería de la ... su conmoción por el atentado en Manchester
El famoso esmalte 'Ballet Slippers' es uno de los colores imprescindibles para la marca Essie. Es un rosa suave, de la gama de los neutros, perfecto para lucir una manicura elegante y chic. Además, es uno de los favoritos de Essie Weingarten, fundadora de la marca y tiene una historia increíble detrás. 
“Essie Weingarten siempre quiso ser una bailarina. Fue su sueño de niña y desde entonces es una apasionada del ballet y ... un esmalte de uñas con el nombre 'Ballet Slippers' que perdurara en el tiempo y le recordara a su niñez. Essie se atrevió a mezclar hasta encontrar la tonalidad perfecta que evocara la dulzura y la delicadeza de las zapatillas de ... como ella misma afirma, el tono 'Ballet Slippers' siempre tendrá preferencia en su corazón”, asegura el sitio de la reconocida marca Essiees.

(@miki_6021)さんの、
「フィギュアスケートの衣装をイメージしたネイル⛸⛸」を紹介します
.
〜やり方〜
①水色の指
2度ぬりし、シルバーのアートペンで掠れ気味に斜めの線を引く。クリア系のホログラムをちょんちょんと貼る。

②ネイビーの指
2度ぬり。

③中指
ベースのシアーピンクを1度ぬり。左右に水色とネイビーをやや細めの筆でぬる。シルバーのアートペンで色の境目のガタつきを隠すようにラインを描く。たっぷりめにトップコートをぬり、スワロフスキーとブリオンをやや埋め込むかんじでのせる。
.
〜使用したもの〜
ネイビー:TiNS 020 the mercury
水色:essie 857 Find Me An Oasis
シアーピンク:essie 473 Sugar Daddy
スワロフスキー:モンタナss5、シルバーシェイドss5
クリア系丸ホログラム1㎜
シルバーブリオン
.
〜ポイント〜
荒川静香さんの「トゥーランドット」の衣装をイメージしたネイルです✨
中指の2色をぬり分けるときは、先に「ラインの中心となる点」「逆三角形の残る頂点2つ」「レンズ型の爪先の点と曲線の中点2つ」を決めて点を打っておきます。私は白の油性ボールペンを使ってます。点を目標に輪郭をとれば狙いどおりにぬりやすいですよ（*'∀'人）♥*+
.

chilling at home  happy friday x Tagged: @benefitcosmetics, @toofaced, @marshalls, @michaelsstores, @houseoflashes, @bobbibrown, @essiepolish, @flatlaysquad, @flatlays, @flatlayforever, @benefitmexico, @whiteaddicted, @onthetable_project, @lancomeofficial, @flatlaystyle, @flatlay_tips, @flatlay_collective, @flatlay, @flatlaytoday, @hashtag.whitefeeds

.
～やり方～
ベースのシアーピンク1度ぬり。
↓
グラデーションするポリッシュを爪先だけ細くぬっておく。超極細フレンチのイメージで。ここで厚みがでてしまうと仕上がりが綺麗にならないので、欲張らずサラッと。
↓
グラデ用にポリッシュを薄める。（お弁当のおかずカップやペットボトルのふたなど）結構たっぷりめに薄め液を入れて、1滴程度のポリッシュを混ぜる。全面にぬる。
↓
薄めたポリッシュの残りにさらに1滴ポリッシュを足して爪の半分くらいをぬる★
↓
ぬる面積を減らしながら★の作業を繰り返す。
↓
表面のラメの凹凸をカバーし、うるつや感を出すため、たっぷりめにトップコートする。
.
～使用したもの～
グラデーション:TiNS 76 the sweetest romance
ベースのシアーピンク:essie 473 Sugar Daddy
スワロフスキー:ローズSS9, ホワイトオパールSS9, クリソライトSS5, オーロラSS5
.
～ポイント～
ラメグラデに凹凸・段差・厚みが出ないように、ある程度乾いてきたら指の腹でそっと抑えます。この一手間で仕上がりがずっと綺麗になると思います♡
.

Breastfeeding has been going well although I did discover that Essie has a posterior tongue tie. It was borderline as to whether it needed to be divided or not, and would ... quickly on the NHS if I had wanted to. However, with some breastfeeding support I have been able to adjust Essie's attachment to the breast well enough that now most of her feeds are trouble-free. Essie currently enjoys sleeping in her Sleepyhead Deluxe, both during the night and her daytime naps. She has a SnuzPod but ... wherever we are in the house so she is always sleeping near me. I have had a few nights where Essie just wouldn't settle at all. We discovered that she seemed to like rave music (don't ask!) and from that I ... that she might like white noise. 3中指

.

水色:essie 857 Find Me An Oasis

スワロフスキー:モンタナss5、シルバーシェイドss5
クリア系丸ホログラム1mm
シルバーブリオン
.
〜ポイント〜
荒川静香さんの「トゥーランドット」の衣装をイメージしたネイルです✨
中指の2色をぬり分けるときは、先に「ラインの中心となる点」「逆三角形の残る頂点2つ」「レンズ型の爪先の点と曲線の中点2つ」を決めて点を打っておきます。私は白の油性ボールペンを使ってます。点を目標に輪郭をとれば狙いどおりにぬりやすいですよ(*'∀'人)♥*+
.

ベースのシアーピンクを丁寧に2度ぬり。
↓
トップコート(セシェヴィート)を薄くぬって完全に乾かす。
↓
セロテープ2枚を使って、ダブルフレンチの根元側用にマスキングする。
↓
化粧用スポンジにぬったイエローのマルチカラーラメをポンポンとおさえるようにして2枚のテープの間を色づける。
↓
そぉっとテープをはがす。
↓
ダブルフレンチの爪先側をレモンイエローでぬる。
↓
ぬり足りないところを細筆でうめる。
↓
たっぷりめにトップコートしてからすかさずパーツをのせる。やや埋め込む感じ。
↓
パーツの上から軽くトップコートする。
.
〜使用したもの〜
ベース:essie 473 Sugar Daddy
イエローのラメポリッシュ:TiNS 47 the yummy milk shake
レモンイエロー:OPI T73 One Chic Chick
.
〜ポイント〜
ダブルフレンチの幅をできるだけ同じにすること、爪全体の長さに対してフレンチの面接比が3分の1程度になるようにすることがバランス良く見えるコツです。そしてフレンチ2色の配色を同系色にすると、すっきり綺麗な印象のダブルフレンチになると思います٩(๑❛ᴗ❛๑)۶♡
.

ぬる面積を減らしながら★の作業を繰り返す。
↓
表面のラメの凹凸をカバーし、うるつや感を出すため、たっぷりめにトップコートする。
.

Q+A With Essie’s 2017 Grand Prize Winner Meagan Knight Los Angeles-based Meagan Knight is the grand prize winner of the 2017 Essie’s Nail Art Awards. After months of design submissions, get to know the nail artist who reigned supreme and find out how the Essie’s helped her grow personally. 

Nail It!: Are you a nail pro or is this a passion project?
Meagan Knight: I’m definitely not a pro, this is entirely a passion project! 
N.I: When you found out about The Essie’s what was your first thought? And how did you decide to enter?
M.K: I found out about the essie’s last year through essie’s Instagram account. I actually entered last year and didn’t even make the top 10, and with good reason–my entry was ... deadline by two weeks and knew it was a sign that I had to enter!
RELATED: Meet Harli Hall, 1st Essie’s Winner and 2016 Nail Art Ambassador
N.I: How did you end up choosing your final design for the entry video? ... it was going to be like, and truthfully, it was the greatest weekend I could have asked for. Everyone at essie was so welcoming and easy-going. The video shoot was a blast, the food was unparalleled, and I was even able ... to be a tourist and visit with some of my best friends in my down time.
READ MORE: Advice from Essie’s Nail Art Awards Judge Michelle Saunders
N.I: What about favorite design?
M.K: My plant cells! My pride and joy! Background: ... great impression. I wanted to validate that I could work with any or all six colors and surpass whatever challenge essie could throw at me. I must have come up with over 30 different designs. I was three days away from ... appreciate their help. I am so grateful for them! This competition helped me realize I am lucky beyond words.

「夜に咲く白い花」を紹介します
.
~やり方~
キャンドゥのホイルネイルシート(ブルーからネイビーにグラデになっているタイプ)をあらかじめハサミでカットしておく✂️1
↓
茄子紺を丁寧に2度ぬり。
↓
半乾きになったら1をピンセットで貼る。真ん中長め、両サイド短めになるように。
↓
ここで一度トップコートする。ホイルとお花シールの間にトップコートを挟むことで奥行きが出るので。
↓
トップコートがしっかり乾いたらお花シールを貼る。お花の端がツンツン浮いてこないように花びら先端をようじなどでしっかりおさえる。
↓
最後にもう一度トップコートをぬる。
.
~使用したもの~
茄子紺:essie 859 Under The Twilight
トップコート:セシェヴィート
.
~ポイント~
茄子紺にのせたブルーグラデのホイル、トップコートを挟んでのせたお花と、奥行きが出るようにしています。奥行きがあるとダークカラーも不思議と透明感を感じる仕上がりになるようです✨
.

What's in a name? The story behind Essie's name... Whenever we tell anyone Essie's name we always receive lots of wonderfully positive comments. People tell us how pretty and unusual a name it is. And we totally agree, it is such a gorgeous name! But unlike her brothers, there is a story behind Essie's name. We didn't choose it just because we loved it, which is why we chose Noah and Jude. There is ... had great-grandparents! I spent a lot of my school holidays with my great-grandparents, Stan and Jess, short for Stanley and Jessie. I adored my Nan and Grandad. I loved them more than anyone in the entire world. They made me feel ... wanted her to be named after my Nan in some way, but I didn't want to name her Jess or Jessie or even Jessica. I was pondering using her name as a middle name, when I heard the name Essie one day and fell in love. I searched online for the origins of the name: a French baby name meaning ... perfect name.I love typographical prints for the children and the boys already have a few different ones featuring their names. Essie doesn't have her own room yet but I have been collecting pictures and ornaments for when she does. This print from The Jam Tart is Essie's first piece of personalised artwork and has whimsical animal letters spelling out her name. Her print has an elephant, a ... story behind your baby's name?Find me on Bloglovin, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook, Pinterest and Google+With thanks to Apples & Pips for Essie's beautiful print.

Essie at 3 Months Old Essie turning three months old has been quite an emotional point in her little life for me. She isn't a newborn ... it's still a bittersweet milestone in my wonderful journey through motherhood. If you read my birth story you'll know that Essie was born at home and she weighed a chunky 9lb 4.5oz. She weighed at 12lb 4oz at two months old ... I needn't have worried though as she just sort of shouted a little in shock but then immediately started smiling again!Essie's hair has stopped falling out now (I wish I could say the same about mine!) and she has some very ... has blue eyes, but I'm still hoping they'll go green like mine! After discovering her hands during her second month, Essie has mastered the ability to grab at things, albeit not very gracefully. She has an firm grip once she gets ... to sleep, just like she is in this video, it's so cute to see! Breastfeeding is still going well and Essie feeds around every four hours or so. I'm not hugely worried about her dropping a centile on the weight growth ... I don't want her to drop any further. We'll see if it makes any difference when I next get her weighed!Essie loves to nap and will often fall asleep in the car or pushchair. If we are at home she likes to go into her rocker for a nap. Amazingly I have been having lots of nights with Essie sleeping through. She has been falling asleep in her rocker downstairs at around 8pm, I take her up to bed ... is why her weight gain has slowed down as she hasn't been having as many night feeds... Essie As If! Fall Collection 
Een collectie geïnspireerd op de 90’s? Yes, please! Ik ben dol op alles uit de 90’s en deze Essie nagellak collectie sprak me dan ook meteen aan. Essie As If! wordt vormgegeven door kleurtjes als snoeperig lichtroze, maar ook metallic paars. Thought the 90’s were over? As if!


Essie As If! – Mixtaupe
Mixtaupe is een kleurtje dat ieder seizoen kan, en bij iedere situatie past. Het is een off white kleur, met ietwat beige ondertoon. Dekt in twee laagjes.

Essie As If! – Saved By The Belle
Aaah, deze nagellak! Ik was gigantisch fan van Saved by the Bell (en ... eerste crush), en ook het kleurtje van deze lak is helemaal mijn ding. Love it all! Dekt in twee laagjes.

Essie As If! – As If!
Ook een prachtig kleurtje, deze As If! nagellak. Hemelsblauw met een héél klein beetje indigo in de verte. Deze nagellak dekt in twee laagjes.

Essie As If! – Girly Grunge
Girly Grunge is de enige metallic lak in de As If! collectie. Deze koele lila tint bevat een zilverachtige glans en dekt in twee laagjes. Girly Grunge is wat streperig tijdens het lakken.

Essie As If! – Knee-high Life
Knee-high Life draag ik op het moment en is een echte herfstkleur. Warm, donkerrood is ... altijd goed in het najaar! Deze lak is wel aan de dikke kant, maar dekt daardoor eigenlijk in één laagje.

Essie As If! – Dressed To The Nineties
Deze kleur lijkt zo op het eerste oog misschien niet heel bijzonder, maar ... best gedaan. Hier zie je een beetje van de glitters. Deze lak dekt in één laagje.

Conclusie
Ik vind de Essie As If! collectie voor de herfst ontzettend leuk! Eigenlijk zijn alle kleuren helemaal mijn ding, behalve de metallic paarse Girly ... De nagellakjes zijn van goede kwaliteit en blijven met topcoat zo’n vijf dagen mooi zitten.
Prijs en verkrijgbaarheid
Je kunt Essie onder andere bij Etos kopen, of online bij Bol.com*. De nagellak kost €9,99 per stuk.
* Deze producten heb ik ontvangen ter review. De link met het sterretje is een affiliate link.

Thought the 90s were over? as if! | Essie herfst ’17 
Toen ik de naam van de Essie collectie voor deze herfst las, wist ik dat ik hem wel móest reviewen. Geboren in 1992 ben ik een echt ... dat dat zou gebeuren, maar nu het toch zo ver is vind ik het eigenlijk best leuk! 
De collectie van Essie ademt jaren 90, met lila tinten, metallic finishes en geweldige namen als ‘as if!’ en ‘saved by the bell’.
Essie nagellak € 9,99
Op alle foto’s draag ik twee lagen nagellak.

mixetaupe
Fris en flets tegelijk. 

saved by the belle ... een andere kleur. Glittertjes, metallic, felle kleuren... Geweldig was dat. Dat gevoel krijg ik met deze collectie weer helemaal terug. 
Essie weet de jaren 90 terug te halen met deze gevarieerde tinten nagellak. Die stuk voor stuk perfect lakken, dekken en snel opdragen. Wederom een geslaagde collectie van Essie. Oh, en mocht je de film Clueless nog nooit gezien hebben: hij staat op Netflix!
